  "text": "Northern blot analyses were performed essentially as previously described [CITATION_1] . For northern blots, 10 µg of total RNA was purified from various human and mouse tissues, separated on a 1.2% agarose gel, and blotted on to nylon Hybond-C membrane (Amersham). Northern blots were probed with randomly primed 32 P-labeled mouse clone 230 cDNA. All hybridizations were performed under high-stringency conditions [CITATION_2] .",
